HEADWORD: Tannage
<hw>Tan"nage</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A tanning; the act,
operation, or result of tanning.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They should have got his cheek fresh <qex>tannage</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>R. Browning.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tannate</ent>⟦br⟧
